Line:
You were <i>so</i> fast with those keys. &lt;They prepare 
       to kiss, but are interrupted by Kramer and his girlfriend coming out of 
       Jerry's bedroom, laughing and horsing around.&gt;

This is so exciting! Look, I have goosebumps! &lt;To Jerry&gt; 
       Touch! Touch them! &lt;Jerry touches her arm. Toby screeches with excitement.&gt; 
       I've never been to a comedy club before!

Oh yeah, we don't want some jerk sitting in front of us, it'll 
       be like, 'Hey, big head, can you move out of the way? I didn't pay a cover 
       charge to stare at your bald spot.' &lt;laughs&gt;

Hey, don't embarrass me today. I got some friends in the stands. 
       &lt;George makes a swinging motion with an imaginary bat and pulls something 
       in his back.&gt;

Justin Pitt, this is Elaine Benes. &lt;Elaine turns around. With 
       sunglasses and a scarf on her head, she bears a close resemblance to Jackie 
       O.&gt;

Oh yeah, I know all about make-up sex, and I'm really sorry. 
       &lt;Shoves George into the hallway and closes the door. George blocks 
       the door with his foot.&gt;

No, not at all. No problem. &lt;Jerry looks at Lena suspiciously. 
       Lena leaves with all of Kramer's poker buddies, who are filing out of 
       Kramer's apartment.&gt;

Look at you. I told you. Up all night playing poker. Come on. 
       &lt;Jerry and George are about to leave. George turn's back and looks 
       at Kramer.&gt;

Our policy is, we're comfortable with our bodies. You know, 
             if someone wants to help themselves to an eyefull, well, we say, 
             'Enjoy the show.'
